data.description: Look no further, you're Home!Beautiful 5 bed 3 full bath with oversize 2 car garage. Over 3000 ft. of living space meticulously cared for in the heart of the Acreage! The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances,granite counter tops,and wood cabinets.Newer hot water heater, 1,200 gallon septic tank recently serviced, new fence, n. 5th bedroom has a private full bath/exterior door perfect for in laws suit.Beautiful neutral ceramic tile throughout the main living areas. Newer aqua soft water system with fully covered an lighted enclosure. Full set of hurricane panels. 3 year old cement driveway. Newer AC unit in the main living area. Over 1 acre of fenced in land. Playground and trampoline included on the sale. Newer 20x20 oversize covered patio. Gorgeous saltwater pool and spa.
